headline: How Recent Developments Are Reshaping the Viatris Investment Story
summary: Viatris stock has seen its Fair Value Estimate rise slightly from $11.43 to $11.88 per share, reflecting cautious optimism among analysts. This modest increase follows incremental improvements in the company's revenue growth forecast and a positive response to new product rollouts.
